{"tid":2395070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"感謝黨！元朗黃泥墩驗出非洲（中國）豬瘟！","createTime":"2021-02-04T15:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T16:15:06.000Z","uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32e0e3a7829da1cba8d555972910f60ec3c0dd99","tid":2395070,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210204/PFXJ7OL4YJGPJANJV53D2BAGPU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210204%2FPFXJ7OL4YJGPJANJV53D2BAGPU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3D&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=5b695218\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210204%2FPFXJ7OL4YJGPJANJV53D2BAGPU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3D&h=2aa0e2ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210204/PFXJ7OL4YJGPJANJV53D2BAGPU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情未平，另一邊廂非洲豬瘟亦靜靜殺到。漁護署表示，於元朗黃泥墩一個持牌豬場檢測出非洲豬瘟病毒，共有6隻豬隻染病，全部均位於同一豬舍，豬舍內共約240隻豬均會被銷毀。署方已即時禁止有關豬場運出任何豬隻，直至另行通知，亦已派員巡查該豬場，並從場內不同豬舍抽取豬隻樣本檢測。漁護署指，今次個案不會影響本地屠房運作，亦不影響整體活豬供應，並強調非洲豬瘟不會傳染給人類，豬肉煮熟後，市民仍可放心食用。"},{"pid":"0a8598134307df36aabe4a6a2e6ae60511aa2bc9","tid":2395070,"uid":78243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"死賤種又係到污名化其他國家"},{"pid":"4d2b1d1753c2349c68b036f0281a29a83dcc6c92","tid":2395070,"uid":271485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"圍村地方，恭賀。"},{"pid":"206534765787290aaec8afdf892095ba35134ee1","tid":2395070,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T16:15:06.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟好似蠢啲<br />\n仲未變種人傳人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}